rows.label: bf06470100_0010
rows.name: So it's a site of a fight against him...

rows.label: bf06470100_0020
rows.name: Say, what are these Devices, anyway?

rows.label: bf06470100_0040
rows.name:
We've never even seen Siren, just
that light thing it shoots down.

rows.label: bf06470100_0050
rows.name:
The God's sword. It's a power granted to the Holy Grail,
sleeping in Eden.

rows.label: bf06470100_0060
rows.name: M-maybe Eden is actually a pretty terrifying place...

rows.label: bf06470100_0090
rows.name:
All that I can find in the corners of my memory
is that townscape...

rows.label: bf06470100_0100
rows.name: Why did God create me, or the Devices...

rows.label: bf06470100_0105
rows.name: That's what I want to find out...

rows.label: bf06470100_0120
rows.name: It's OK. We'll find out once we get there.

rows.label: bf06470100_0140
rows.name: Open a chest, it might turn out great...

rows.label: bf06470100_0145
rows.name: But until then, it's just a crate!

rows.label: bf06470100_0150
rows.name: That's rule 4 of the Salvager's Code! Haha.

rows.label: bf06470100_0170
rows.name:
Comparing Eden to
dirty old sea junk...
